{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A treacherous visual novel about friendship, desire, and grief.</h2><br><br>What\u2019s better than a sensual summer retreat in the South of Italy? Join Claudio, Andrea, and Mida in their travels as they try to recover from the collective trauma of the 2020 pandemic.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103680/extras/bus.gif?t=1727787632\" /><br><br>Three young men in their early 20s reconnect after two years of forced isolation, hoping to rekindle their friendship; an exceptional bond that made the trio truly special! A mythological force well beyond the sum of its parts! Or so they think\u2026 <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103680/extras/market.gif?t=1727787632\" /><br><br>As you pick their activities for the day, you\u2019ll discover their darkest fears, their obsessions, and, as the reality of their failed expectations become apparent, their thirst for revenge and retribution.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103680/extras/beachpool.gif?t=1727787632\" /><br><br>A lazy afternoon by the pool, a lustful night at the club, or even a morbid visit to the local cemetery: you\u2019ll decide how to spend this summer vacation, but wherever you go, something or someone will be waiting, offering an additional, forbidden trip through the arcane inner spaces of conscience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103680/extras/fruit.gif?t=1727787632\" /><br><br><br><strong>Eat the Fruit of Mirages and fight for your endless summer!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HIGHLIGHTS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick daily activities for the trio and see how they affect the story.<br></li><li>A new treacherous drama from the creator of Milky Way Prince \u2013 The Vampire Star.<br></li><li>A generational story that is as touching as it is disturbing.<br></li><li>With music, writing, and art from the game\u2019s author, including hundreds and hundreds of original illustrations.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103680/extras/dialogue.gif?t=1727787632\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">INFO</h2>A playthrough lasts 3 to 4 hours, reaching one of many possible endings and showing roughly 60% of the game\u2019s content.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Puglia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/3ba137e5a97697c7ca9357e37cb305e076af20af.jpg"},{"name":"The Tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/c85a10cd6a835c8ded98c62f54b4e3c6c28143f3.jpg"},{"name":"Pump It Up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/161dcca70fedd54c5ce56ca27bfb2269ee799f55.jpg"},{"name":"Cloistered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/4f73a71ea1b85caf4584f45a0746ec68153449aa.jpg"},{"name":"Stand-off","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/2b8090a7492bcc0a0544b25e22c8a95782e1c36d.jpg"},{"name":"Sell the Essence","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/13864e4b8c2f4d076ac95f0d8d2efc6001409ffd.jpg"},{"name":"I Ragazzi del Sole","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/aa13ae281cb18a138224aa7ddca511191f9d03cb.jpg"},{"name":"Crisis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/46d364577e7fe4d9d85862d6959de88494ed9ac7.jpg"},{"name":"Heritage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103680/1cb51b84836d9c8ff8ce24c6bc62f5c809972fd3.jpg"},{"name":"No Thanks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommuni